  "worklog": "## 2026-03-30 08:08 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 3] V5 Tiered Sizing Design + Growth Projection\n\n**Task:** Design balance-adaptive position sizing for V5. Model compounding growth from current $922 through Phase 3 ($50-100/day).\n\n**Finding:** At 65% WR, avg price 0.51, current sizing ($12/trade):\n- Expected profit per trade: $3.29\n- At ~8 trades/day: **$26.30/day expected** (matches W13 actual: $30.91/day)\n- Current sizing is optimal for $922 balance but will underperform as balance grows\n\n**V5 Tiered Sizing Model:**\n\n| Balance | Max % | Trade Size | Avg Profit/Trade | Trades for $50/day |\n|---------|-------|------------|------------------|--------------------|\n| $500 | 1.2% | $6.60 | $1.81 | 28 (impossible) |\n| $750 | 1.3% | $10.73 | $2.94 | 17 (hard) |\n| **$1,000** | **1.4%** | **$15.40** | **$4.23** | **12 (feasible)** |\n| $1,500 | 1.5% | $24.75 | $6.79 | 7.4 (easy) |\n| $2,000 | 1.6% | $35.20 | $9.66 | 5.2 (2 hours) |\n\n**Compounding projection (3%/day, weekdays only):**\n- Week 1: $1,069 \u2192 Phase 2 secured\n- Week 4: $1,666 \u2192 Phase 3 approaching\n- Week 8: $3,009 \u2192 Phase 3 achieved ($90/day)\n\n**Decision:** V5 tiered sizing patch written (`patches/v5-tiered-sizing.patch.md`). Deploy when:\n1. V4.1 proves stable for 1 week\n2. WR sustains \u2265 60%\n3. Balance crosses $1,000\n\nThe key growth lever: at $1,000 with V5 sizing, we need only 12 trades/day for $50/day. With 4 active hours and VWAP relaxation adding ~3 extra trades/day, 12 trades is achievable.\n\n**Next P3 heartbeat:** After V4.1 trades Monday, recalculate actual WR and trades/hour. Determine if 12 trades/day is realistic with current filter settings.\n\n## 2026-03-30 07:38 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 2] Pre-Session Analysis: Regime Dropping to RANGE by 11h\n\n**Task:** Analyze market conditions for upcoming V4.1 first active hour (11h UTC). Build pre-session check tool.\n\n**Finding:**\n1. **Regime shifting TREND \u2192 RANGE:** My regime_classifier shows RANGE (score 3-4/10). The bot's internal filter currently reads TREND (score 3/6) because the $65K\u2192$67.5K crash candles are still in its 8h lookback. By 11h UTC, those candles roll out:\n   - Recent 5h range: 0.67% (under 1.0% threshold = 0 points)\n   - Recent consistency: 0.60 (under 0.625 = 0 points)\n   - **Projected 11h regime: RANGE (score 0/6) \u2192 bot WILL trade \u2705**\n\n2. **Market consolidating perfectly:** BTC in tight $67,277-$67,581 range for 5 hours. Low volume (0.58x normal). This is textbook RANGE \u2014 exactly where our contrarian strategy thrives.\n\n3. **Built `scripts/pre-session-check.sh`** \u2014 one-command health check before active hours:\n   - Bot alive? \u2705 | STOP_TRADING? \u2705 none | Balance: $922.45\n   - Regime: RANGE | BTC: $67,305 | F&G: 8 (Extreme Fear)\n   - V4.1 config confirmed: F&G +0.05 edge, 1.10x size\n\n**My thinking:** Conditions are ideal for V4.1's first live test:\n- RANGE regime = our 71% WR zone\n- Extreme Fear F&G = contrarian edge present\n- Low volatility = clean signals, less noise\n- 11h/12h = our 88%/82% WR hours with VWAP relaxation active\n\nIf V4.1 performs as expecte",
